info.title: OX REST API
info.description:
Documentation of the Open-Xchange REST API.

___

parameters.name: context-group
parameters.description: The context group identifying the global DB where the feedback is stored.

parameters.name: start
parameters.description: Start time in seconds since 1970-01-01 00:00:00 UTC. Only feedback given after this time is deleted. If not set, all feedback up to -e is deleted.

parameters.name: end
parameters.description: End time in seconds since 1970-01-01 00:00:00 UTC. Only feedback given before this time is deleted. If not set, all feedback since -s is deleted.

200.description: Blank in case of success, error message from server in case of error.

400.description: Bad request, response contains error message.
